Package net.bitnine.agensgraph.ext.agtype

Interface AgtypeMap

  • public interface AgtypeMap
    Non-Mutable Map of Agtype values. This implementation provides partial implementation of map operations, and permits null values, but not null keys. This class makes no guarantees as to the order of the map; in particular, it does not guarantee that the order will remain constant over time.
    Since:
    0.0.1
    See Also:
    AgtypeMapBuilder
